[Student "S"]
{WEST thinks they should be in slam, and uses Stayman to check for a 4-4 Major fit.

When EAST announces four \Ss WEST uses RKCB 4NT.

EAST's 5\S bid shows two Key Cards plus the \SQ.

This fills the holes in WEST's hand nicely, so she bids 6\S.}

