[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/roman_key_card"]
[Student "S"]
{This is the companion hand to Deal 18.

Again, NORTH uses RKCB after the 4-4 \S fit is discovered. 
This time SOUTH shows two Key Cards without the \SQ.

Now NORTH realizes that in addition to one outside Ace, there is a very possible loser 
in trumps. So she stops at 5\S.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "4"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "All"]
[Deal "E:732.AKQ864.53.87 QT8.32.T42.QJ962 AK4.J95.AK76.A54 J965.T7.QJ98.KT3"]
